g.text: cobib(1) -- a console-based bibliography management tool
coBib is a console-based bibliography management tool written in Python. It
maintains a plain-text database of literature references in YAML format and
provides various subcommands to work with this database. It also provides an
its command-line interface (see the [SUBCOMMANDS][] section below).
